{"tid":1428082,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋係有底線同原則 （中佬勤諫）","createTime":"2019-08-07T08:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:46:29.000Z","uid":71816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"817babfb17d8a4de5d29ba5dd34284c12ec690b3","tid":1428082,"uid":71816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:46:29.000Z","msg":"求下大家  可唔可以搵人幫我擺上連登<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n擺咗啦，PS. 好多中壯年好想同我哋We connect 先搵我哋有ac嘅幫手po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登有愛</span></span> <strong>溫柔地話返俾佢哋知你哋係點諗啦</strong>  好，開波！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n個人認為&mdash;示威應該保持嘅<ins><strong>八大</strong></ins>原則<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>我哋唔係警犬</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋係有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">道德底線</span></span> <br />\n與怪物戰鬥應該小心自己<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好變成怪物</strong></span></strong>[/size=4]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好陷入路西法效應</span><br />\n而家唔係同前線割<br />\n只係希望前線可以做得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更好</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民意對於社運真係好重要好重要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好L重要</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>街坊落街鬧狗都係因為佢哋<del>冇民意</del></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.不殺人<br />\n2.不打平民（當然如果佢係攻擊性嘅你可以綁住佢但千祈唔好用私刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n3.不破壞非政府建築<br />\n<br />\n4.火淨係攞嚟掩護撤退<br />\n如非必要真係唔好用<br />\n<br />\n我哋之所以有民意支持<br />\n係因為我哋早期示威嘅種種友善行為<br />\n你放火的煙供上去老人院同埋小朋友<br />\n同黑警有乜分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.唔好搞唔係純粹警察嘅宿舍<br />\n<br />\n海關消防呢啲紀律部隊都有好多人支持我哋<br />\n你估下你搞著佢屋企人佢仲撐唔撐我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. Be water 唔洗解釋啦<br />\n<br />\n7.唔好搞歷史文物<br />\n就好似我哋唔破壞立法會入邊啲書同默默噉樣，呢啲係港人嘅共同財產<br />\n<br />\n8.見到有市民影相<br />\n咁儘可能客氣地阻止佢<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />溫柔係我哋最大嘅武器</span></strong><br />\n（排版、字眼經過本人稍作編輯）"}]}